Fast-Food Operational Excellence & Growth

Project Overview: You are a BI Consultant for a regional fast-food chain. The executive team needs a data-driven strategy to improve Net Profit and customer satisfaction. You will use the provided dataset of 1,000 transactions to deliver actionable insights.

Core Requirements:

Data Cleaning & ETL:
Convert OrderDate to a proper datetime format.
Verify NetProfit accuracy across all rows.

EDA:
Identify the highest and lowest performing StoreLocation by total revenue.
Analyze OrderCancellation rates to identify operational bottlenecks.

Customer Insights:
Determine which MarketingChannel (e.g., Social Media, Email, TV) yields the highest AOV.
Evaluate if the CustomerLoyaltyTier system effectively correlates with higher spending.

Quality & Safety Analysis:
Assess the relationship between HealthInspectionScore and CustomerFeedbackScore.

Final Output:
A functional dashboard in Power BI or Tableau.
A brief summary report outlining three specific recommendations for the management team.
